$ ----------------------------------------------------------------------
$ Cantilever plate with a central RBE2 spider -- SOL 101
$
$ Demonstrates:
$   - Mixed CQUAD4 + CTRIA3 mesh (exercises the v5.0.0 shell-bucket
$     split: shell_q4 + shell_tri3 sub-buckets).
$   - RBE2 rigid spider distributing tip load to a column of nodes.
$   - Combined SPC + FORCE on a non-trivial mesh.
$
$ Geometry: 10 in x 4 in cantilever plate, t = 0.05 in.
$ Mesh: mostly CQUAD4 with two CTRIA3 cells at the tip.
$ Material: Al 6061-T6.
$ Load: 50 lbf at a spider master node (independent) -> RBE2 transfers
$       to the column of grids at X = 10 in.
$ Constraints: SPC1 123456 at the left edge.
$ ----------------------------------------------------------------------
SOL 101
CEND
TITLE = Cantilever plate with RBE2 spider (mixed quad+tri)
SUBCASE 1
  LOAD = 1
  SPC = 1
  DISPLACEMENT(PRINT,PLOT) = ALL
  STRESS(PRINT,PLOT) = ALL
BEGIN BULK
$
$ -------- Material --------
MAT1           1  9.9+6          .33    .098
$
$ -------- Property (shell, t=0.05) --------
PSHELL         1       1    .05       1               1
$
$ -------- Plate nodes: 5 along X, 3 along Y (15 nodes) --------
GRID           1              0.      0.      0.
GRID           2             2.5      0.      0.
GRID           3              5.      0.      0.
GRID           4             7.5      0.      0.
GRID           5             10.      0.      0.
GRID           6              0.      2.      0.
GRID           7             2.5      2.      0.
GRID           8              5.      2.      0.
GRID           9             7.5      2.      0.
GRID          10             10.      2.      0.
GRID          11              0.      4.      0.
GRID          12             2.5      4.      0.
GRID          13              5.      4.      0.
GRID          14             7.5      4.      0.
GRID          15             10.      4.      0.
$
$ -------- Spider master node (offset 2 in past tip in +X) --------
GRID         100             12.      2.      0.
$
$ -------- Elements: 8 CQUAD4 + 2 CTRIA3 (mixed mesh) --------
$ Bottom row of quads (between y=0 and y=2)
CQUAD4         1       1       1       2       7       6
CQUAD4         2       1       2       3       8       7
CQUAD4         3       1       3       4       9       8
$ Tip column: split last quad into 2 trias to exercise shell_tri3
CTRIA3         4       1       4       5      10
CTRIA3         5       1       4      10       9
$ Top row of quads (between y=2 and y=4)
CQUAD4         6       1       6       7      12      11
CQUAD4         7       1       7       8      13      12
CQUAD4         8       1       8       9      14      13
$ Top tip column: also trias
CTRIA3         9       1       9      10      15
CTRIA3        10       1       9      15      14
$
$ -------- RBE2 spider: master = node 100, slaves = tip nodes 5,10,15 -
$ RBE2,EID,GN,CM,GM1,GM2,GM3
RBE2          50     100  123456       5      10      15
$
$ -------- Constraints (root clamped) --------
SPC1           1  123456       1       6      11
$
$ -------- Load: 50 lbf in -Z at the spider master node --------
FORCE          1     100       0    -50.      0.      0.      1.
$
ENDDATA
